text: Prisca Emeafu (born 30 March 1972) is former football defender. She played for the Nigeria women's national football team. She was in the 1995 FIFA Women's World Cup and 1999 FIFA Women's World Cup. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian footballers Category:1995 FIFA Women's World Cup players Category:1999 FIFA Women's World Cup players Category:Association football defenders
